data.description: This home still smells like a new home, a very well-kept 2017 Milestone home that was bought brand new from the current owners and now moving to West Texas for work and an easier life. Big backyard and a bigger lot than most in this neighborhood because is on the curve of the street. The neighborhood is a nice tidy community and they have seasonal events for everyone to attend. Pool and amenity center and sports courts as well. We are very easy to work with and are open to any offers, come see it for yourself before buying anything else, you will not regret it.
